Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.51,0:02:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件衣服 是聖誕老人的衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.76,0:02:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 每年籐本君都會扮成聖誕老人的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.46,0:02:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不扮還有誰能扮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.76,0:02:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢 拜託了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.44,0:03:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}[...白色聖誕節.]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.62,0:03:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐本先生 還在生我的氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.08,0:03:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.45,0:03:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.40,0:03:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這種事來 你應該明白的吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.31,0:03:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.57,0:03:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金平糖啊金平糖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.05,0:03:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.37,0:03:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.43,0:03:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.11,0:03:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂元先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.96,0:03:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在等你呢 忙到這麼晚辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.37,0:03:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 我很精神的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.18,0:03:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送你回家吧 如果你不嫌麻煩的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.39,0:03:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會 非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.92,0:03:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕節到處都閃閃發光 太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.90,0:03:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.68,0:03:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩 有什麼想要的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.82,0:03:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要的東西啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.78,0:03:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.10,0:03:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新玩具已經用義賣會的錢買了...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.64,0:03:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.94,0:04:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我可以為小鳩選一件合適的東西嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.32,0:04:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.31,0:04:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.67,0:04:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.95,0:04:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是聖誕節嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.54,0:04:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選什麼才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.24,0:04:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呦 真辛苦啊 大聖誕節的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.81,0:04:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒啊 跟什麼聖誕節無關啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.67,0:04:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.46,0:04:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.18,0:04:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.66,0:04:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.52,0:04:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.30,0:04:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩 你還沒有跟清和和好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.51,0:05:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像...被籐本先生討厭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.07,0:05:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐本先生和平時不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.51,0:05:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像平時那樣數落我 連看都不看我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.46,0:05:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.12,0:05:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事 讓我總也無法釋懷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.58,0:05:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩沒有錯 清和一定也是這樣想的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.60,0:05:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過沒法坦白地說出來而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不用擔心的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.98,0:05:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.36,0:05:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.20,0:05:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.54,0:05:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天也能見到你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.45,0:05:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.75,0:05:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我等你 在保育園門口
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.48,0:05:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那多冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.71,0:05:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.12,0:06:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.95,0:06:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.07,0:06:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 明天再見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.62,0:06:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.53,0:06:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家裡也到聖誕節啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.66,0:06:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 也得為五百祗先生準備禮物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.11,0:06:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.47,0:06:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金平糖 一滿瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.94,0:06:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.84,0:06:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.69,0:06:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 是為五百祗先生做的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.44,0:06:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.53,0:06:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 五百祗先生變成馴鹿先生了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.47,0:06:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土鳩!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.08,0:06:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.70,0:07:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 遲到了!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.31,0:07:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.40,0:07:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天比平時都早呢小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.40,0:07:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 要為聖誕會做準備
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.68,0:07:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.00,0:07:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩 今晚沒有預定的話就來我家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要開聖誕會的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.26,0:07:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽會做好多好吃的的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.48,0:07:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.76,0:07:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果方便的話就請過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.32,0:07:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.61,0:07:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.02,0:07:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.65,0:07:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐本先生方便的話也來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.92,0:07:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家的聖誕會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上我要打工的 而且聖誕節...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.04,0:07:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工加油哦 慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 你們也得快點出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.59,0:08:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.52,0:08:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.68,0:08:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕節大家都高高興興的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.88,0:08:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有籐本先生好像很悲傷的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.12,0:08:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是因為之前我做了多餘的事...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.63,0:08:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.17,0:08:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.23,0:08:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清和君他...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.47,0:08:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在聖誕前夜之後...變成了孤兒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.54,0:08:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}(Merry Xmas! 給媽媽)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.47,0:09:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 媽媽!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.85,0:09:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.06,0:09:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.98,0:09:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.58,0:09:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.65,0:10:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清和君的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.71,0:10:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那天起再也沒有回去過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.74,0:10:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後沒過多久
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.83,0:10:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清和君就被清花的父親收養了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.37,0:11:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來晚了 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.38,0:11:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.58,0:11:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 開始聖誕會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.86,0:11:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換好衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.07,0:11:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼籐本君 大家叫你的時候就進來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.90,0:11:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.81,0:11:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.30,0:11:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也換好衣服過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.94,0:11:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.26,0:11:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐本先生...很偉大...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.95,0:11:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.28,0:11:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很偉大...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.65,0:12:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.27,0:12:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.08,0:12:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼大家一起呼喚聖誕老人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.49,0:12:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.86,0:12:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕老人~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.93,0:12:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕老人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.95,0:12:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是聖誕老人...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.77,0:12:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕老人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.50,0:12:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕老人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.86,0:12:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧 清和老師?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.75,0:12:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.53,0:12:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是聖誕老人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.22,0:12:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕老人...是清和老師嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.08,0:12:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是聖誕老人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.24,0:12:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯的吧 聖誕老人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.24,0:13:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.28,0:13:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家會從聖誕老人那裡得到什麼禮物呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.14,0:13:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕老人 禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.83,0:13:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.81,0:13:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.93,0:13:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.00,0:13:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您 聖誕老人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.36,0:13:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.56,0:13:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該一起吃蛋糕了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.63,0:13:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.95,0:13:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去收禮物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.05,0:13:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐本先生 今天辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.77,0:13:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來的收尾工作我會做的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.07,0:13:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 今天是聖誕嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.29,0:13:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你瞎操心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.14,0:14:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 為什麼要我做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.40,0:14:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少廢話 聖誕節才是生意旺季啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.73,0:14:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人做這麼多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.67,0:14:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Merry-Christmas
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.46,0:14:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.41,0:14:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還蠻合適的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.92,0:14:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.40,0:14:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.37,0:15:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊 因為是聖誕節
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.21,0:15:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清和才不開心的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.47,0:15:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...好像反而傷到籐本先生了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.34,0:15:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下...籐本先生更討厭我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.48,0:15:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.95,0:15:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這為什麼會讓我如此痛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.21,0:15:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這麼在意清和嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.50,0:15:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不覺就想著籐本先生的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.99,0:15:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道為什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.51,0:15:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到胸口就很疼...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.65,0:16:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.19,0:16:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂元先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.78,0:16:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給小鳩的最好的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.90,0:16:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在終於知道是什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.20,0:16:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.92,0:16:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是聖誕禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.09,0:16:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.13,0:16:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別誤會 不是給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.82,0:16:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想讓你把它轉交給展望台上的小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.49,0:16:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 這裡我替你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.28,0:16:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊 為什麼要我去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.08,0:16:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大聖誕節的 她卻好像很難過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.10,0:16:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.35,0:16:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被你的態度傷害到的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.79,0:16:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.23,0:17:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩覺得是她自己不好...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.51,0:17:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說想要向你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.44,0:17:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還等在那裡呢 小鳩她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.28,0:17:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人在那裡等著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.59,0:18:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐本先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.63,0:18:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.64,0:18:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有做錯什麼 不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.48,0:18:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.91,0:18:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 幹嘛要這麼介意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.68,0:18:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 難道說 籐本先生沒生氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.00,0:18:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從一開始...我就說了沒生氣的!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.39,0:18:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現 現在就在生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.02,0:18:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 不要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.78,0:18:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.75,0:18:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 堂元給你的 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.13,0:19:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.94,0:19:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和好了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.43,0:19:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我送你的禮物哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.28,0:19:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙要是又刁難你的話 就對不起了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.26,0:19:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.63,0:19:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.45,0:19:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂元先生給我的禮物是籐本先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.36,0:19:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 堂元跟你說什麼了讓你在這等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.18,0:19:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說會帶來非常適合小鳩的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.20,0:19:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂元先生 讓我和籐本先生和好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.59,0:19:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.29,0:19:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.26,0:19:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐本先生 下雪了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.25,0:19:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一看不就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.57,0:19:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.60,0:20:13.18,XXX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}春に咲く花　夏広がる空よ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.60,0:20:13.18,XXX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}春天綻放的鮮花　夏天寬廣的天空哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.19,0:20:27.13,XXX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}心の中に刻まれて煌めく
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.19,0:20:27.13,XXX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}在心中閃閃發光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.71,0:20:40.75,XXX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}朝に降る雨　窓を閉ざす日にも
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.71,0:20:40.75,XXX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}哪怕清晨下起雨　關起窗戶的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.68,0:20:54.52,XXX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}胸にあふれる光は雲の上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.68,0:20:54.52,XXX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}充滿胸中的光在雲層之上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.67,0:21:09.87,XXX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}喜び悲しみ　すべて抱いて歩いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.67,0:21:09.87,XXX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}喜悦與悲傷　懷抱一切不停前行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.18,0:21:24.22,XXX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}私の手と君の手を　強く繋ぐもの
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.18,0:21:24.22,XXX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}因為我和你的手 緊緊握在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.25,0:22:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪原來...這麼美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.39,0:22:35.75,XXX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}わたしを導く　遠い遠い呼び声よ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.39,0:22:35.75,XXX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}引導我的遙遠的聲音啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.62,0:22:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管結果如何 冬天過去春天來臨時...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.72,0:22:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要和小鳩告別了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.03,0:22:50.18,XXX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}微笑むように　歌うように　響く風の音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.03,0:22:50.18,XXX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}好像在微笑好像在歌唱一樣的風聲

Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.18,0:24:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}[...踏上旅途的人.]

Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.98,0:23:08.62,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}人はみな飛んでみたいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.79,0:23:16.05,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}重力に騙されてるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.24,0:23:24.15,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}誰もほんとは飛べるんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.30,0:23:33.19,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}あの子があんなに悲しそうなのは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.57,0:23:43.55,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}自分の影をどこかに忘れてきちゃったからかも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.85,0:23:46.16,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}それなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.48,0:23:50.51,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}ありがとうって　君に言えたら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.68,0:23:54.51,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}ありがとうって　君が笑えば
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.71,0:24:01.90,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}いったりきたり　嬉しくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.27,0:24:06.65,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}君が幸せになる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.88,0:24:11.07,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}心配なんていらないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.24,0:24:15.46,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}一緒にいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.94,0:24:28.24,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}嬉しくても涙が出るなんて不思議だ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.98,0:23:08.62,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}明明人們都是那麼想飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.79,0:23:16.05,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}只不過被重力所欺騙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.24,0:23:24.15,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}其實誰都可以在天上翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.30,0:23:33.19,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}那個孩子為什麼如此悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.57,0:23:43.55,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}也許是把自己的影子忘在了哪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.85,0:23:46.16,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}是那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.48,0:23:50.51,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}如果能對你說 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.68,0:23:54.51,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}如果能看見你的笑容 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.71,0:24:01.90,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}來來往往中 變得愉悅
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.27,0:24:06.65,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}你一定能變得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.88,0:24:11.07,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}不需要擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.24,0:24:15.46,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}因為我們在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.94,0:24:28.24,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}喜極而泣總是那麼不可思議
